{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":183,"question":"平时我们使用圆轴形胶带中总是为找不到头而浪费不少时间，一家公司设计了齿轮轴形的胶带，使用后只要把胶带架在两齿之间，就能很方便找到头。<br/><br/>齿轮轴形的胶带体现了SCAMPER中的哪种思维？<br/>","type":1,"analysis":"Modify 改变产品形状","pic":null,"difficulty":2,"knowledgeId":15,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":3,"sequence":6,"example":false,"practiceUid":"TT003C002F006X01006","score":30,"choiceList":[{"id":559,"questionId":183,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":560,"questionId":183,"subject":"Combine合并","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":561,"questionId":183,"subject":"Adapt适应","sequence":3,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":562,"questionId":183,"subject":"Modify修改","sequence":4,"isRight":true,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":2359,"warmupPracticeId":183,"repliedId":1220,"comment":"圆轴型胶带变成齿轮轴型胶带。\n不是胶带加齿轮，仔细看看。","openid":null,"addTime":1492802754000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"我理解的合并应该是形成了一个新的东西，而目前胶带还是胶带，只是增加了功能。","del":0,"repliedName":"蛋散","name":"炜航 Kevin 秋叶","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6KqibGzDyhKrSPYQHTYNocHEjT32hB0xJhOiahia23djiaFlwfOvgpxAZHia7Je42MZOUj5MvAngcHFWRMz/0","discussTime":"2017-04-22"},{"id":2347,"warmupPracticeId":183,"repliedId":null,"comment":"属性还是胶带，但是样子发生了变化，就是修改","openid":null,"addTime":1492784190000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"王妍","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJicBJlWGxGfthZ9KVpAOicm7icmNCeMIHa6OY0JicjZJJibQtt4hpggTfgfa1I8VWo1tNzddySgWWRJVw/0","discussTime":"2017-04-21"},{"id":2030,"warmupPracticeId":183,"repliedId":null,"comment":"我觉得这个问题中，我有个问题就是并不知道齿轮型胶带是怎么样的。","openid":null,"addTime":1492139704000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"中華包子","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLXaHIafcDEnAiaib5Ax3fan8tiaiaDHTxl9vHiatMlMunqMX0mOTwIFLPNxiaAajFzCajtR6fww20cdbBNg8aDJJFmya/0","discussTime":"2017-04-14"},{"id":1220,"warmupPracticeId":183,"repliedId":1073,"comment":"我理解的合并应该是形成了一个新的东西，而目前胶带还是胶带，只是增加了功能。","openid":null,"addTime":1490106551000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"为什么不能说将胶带和齿轮合并呢？","del":0,"repliedName":"Lillian","name":"蛋散","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLAB5S4ffBIIpicRRfZ68XoawAp5BNp3sxONDmJPribKLgC5x2AxTK4WvbYmfIk27GD6w3KufOnqkZrg/0","discussTime":"2017-03-21"},{"id":1073,"warmupPracticeId":183,"repliedId":null,"comment":"为什么不能说将胶带和齿轮合并呢？","openid":null,"addTime":1489837580000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Lillian","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay0XHFXZiaE04RD4rVbXnWYnib3GQsicILf4AoSPUFoByLb5G32G6Nj7X2vAg8DLOyicEribVwSJQKTWpy/0","discussTime":"2017-03-18"}],"choice":null,"knowledge":{"id":15,"knowledge":"用SCAMPER结构化头脑风暴","step":"结构化思考","analysis":"SCAMPER（由七个英文单词或短语的首字母构成）是一种用于头脑风暴的问题清单，它为普通的头脑风暴提供了更为结构化的指导。通常适用于改进某个产品或服务的情景。","means":"在改进产品或服务时，用以下七个问题一一发问，拓展思路：\nSubstitute（代替）：成分、材料、人员是否有可替代方案，乃至对旧产品、旧服务可以进行替代吗？\nCombine（合并）：资源、品类、功能等是否存在合并的可能？\nAdapt（适应）：产品或服务能适应哪些其他场景？\nModify（修改）：产品的颜色、形状等特征可以作何修改？\nPut to other uses（作为他用）：产品或服务还有哪些新用途吗？\nEliminate（简化）：产品或服务可以做哪些简化？\nReverse（rearrange）（反向、重新安排）：产品或服务可以怎样逆向操作、重新安排？\n","keynote":"SCAMPER问题清单可以使你打开思路、拓展想法，但并非每个问题的答案都适合需要\n","pic":null,"audio":"http://www.iqycamp.com/audio/rise_k15.m4a","appear":0,"example":null}},{"id":185,"question":"利用网页观看视频时，移动鼠标到窗口外，播放的菜单栏就会自动收起。<br/><br/>这种设计体现了SCAMPER中的哪种思维方式？","type":1,"analysis":"Eliminate 将原来的“移动-点击关闭”动作简化为“移动”","pic":null,"difficulty":2,"knowledgeId":57,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":3,"sequence":2,"example":false,"practiceUid":"Y003T003C002A002X01002","score":30,"choiceList":[{"id":573,"questionId":185,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":576,"questionId":185,"subject":"Modify修改","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":577,"questionId":185,"subject":"Put to other uses改作他用","sequence":3,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":578,"questionId":185,"subject":"Eliminate消除","sequence":4,"isRight":true,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":626,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":258,"comment":"我的理解是修改只是把产品的某一或某些具体特征进行重新处理使其发生变化；而简化是把产品的某些特征去掉。就这道题而言，如果是修改的话，鼠标移出窗口和关闭菜单这两个步骤都要有，只是在这两个步骤上做了其它的处理。","openid":null,"addTime":1488691593000,"priority":1,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"修改为啥不对？有些混淆修改与简化的区别了","del":0,"repliedName":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","name":"大头娃娃","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNEvKRFpbeOmYHJcFmkdv2hiaKchUpf7g590IA9HhXv7c4GmX8j4jP25LT0ATygpmZwibqTTOBtHta/0","discussTime":"2017-03-05"},{"id":1465,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":null,"comment":"修改我是这样理解的，之前可能是导航栏无论是鼠标在播放区域内还是外，都存在，现在改成鼠标移动到视频区域外就消失。这是改变形式或者动态的改变外观","openid":null,"addTime":1490670895000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Peter","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoDcHxeWtQYv2UGlg2IxShJKu5E8JdibAXg9Ssfk8Wib8cLL3wZzbbIfIam8O1Va5ic5nOWKqjAElKzG/0","discussTime":"2017-03-28"},{"id":856,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":258,"comment":"可以多看下知识点中的举例说明，来理解题目中修改与简化等词的具体意思，而不要根据平时认为的词的意思来做题","openid":null,"addTime":1489492708000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"修改为啥不对？有些混淆修改与简化的区别了","del":0,"repliedName":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","name":"Chuan","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibamKCK8uuoacbYS5yGavNuEssFugKg6UXLemfUj5nYtsNpFFZY3dOswIaakVONDeQswbqBDTcD32/0","discussTime":"2017-03-14"},{"id":268,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":null,"comment":"越来越迷糊了。第一，这个功能能不能给点图啊？我对移动鼠标-收起菜单栏没什么印象呢〒_〒\n第二，收起菜单栏是为了使用其他程序，是否可以理解为移做他用呢？","openid":null,"addTime":1487922063000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"郭舒简","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XRibESzncllLeNVVgOoXl3jmKXQT07IR1fYwPRIgiboTXU2tjiaAn3zpZ6cp8iaIvcTMxyrcwRR0P62w/0","discussTime":"2017-02-24"},{"id":258,"warmupPrac